title: Dream Alone
info:
[i]Lyrics:

a little girl is dreaming of the sky looking for the love she heard about
she wonders if it's all a lie and then she starts to shout

why can't i have that feeling, why can't i fall in love?
why does noone care what i'm dreaming of?

why can't i find the feeling, why can't i have my love?
is it too much to ask a little girl dreaming of
wonderful butterflies asking me to join them
but then i realized i'm dreaming alone

a little girl is dreaming of the sky looking for the love she heard about
she wonders if it's all a lie and then she starts to shout

why can't i share my feeling, why can i never find my love?
why does noone truly know what i'm dreaming of?[/i]
